{"tid":1918360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對抗武漢肺炎，美國醫療必需品究竟多不足？","createTime":"2020-03-10T04:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T04:53:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90e2972df4aac1f80b4b1c386cb0b50ab1a7a7e2","tid":1918360,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"3億片防護口罩與醫用口罩。這是美國急需的物資，用來保護醫護人員抵禦冠狀病毒的威脅。不過，該國的緊急儲備卻未達這些物資的15%。<br />\n<br />\n美國衛生與公共服務部部長艾力克斯．艾薩（Alex Azar）於2月底在參議院證實，美國國家戰略儲備系統（Strategic National Stockpile）只存有3000萬片外科口罩與1200萬片防護口罩。這個消息令人驚訝，因為出於國家安全理由，該儲備系統的存貨狀況通常不會向外界公布⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUAO0kT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUAO0kT.jpg&h=c0baa735&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZnebsA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZnebsA.jpg&h=42585be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.natgeomedia.com/science/article/content-10796.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natgeomedia.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fcontent-10796.html&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eStDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=f5aac89b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.natgeomedia.com/science/article/content-10796.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcd1da4f75cc12539e5ff1d4b8f71176391834e7","tid":1918360,"uid":83128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T23:30:04.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n連登仔繼續：美國任何衰野都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a0d7e6f712f604cbdf1c5d1c65915d221db5cb","tid":1918360,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"支那近十年發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n2008年果陣人工已經遠超東南亞，反而工廠越來越多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca15c00e2e7b034fe6b88ec2187bc852f75ed95","tid":1918360,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":